17 PE to their earnings which would make their price $1.00/share. Even at a 10
PE the stock should sell for $0.58/share or 89% higher than the current price
of $0.31/share. Thats still a very good risk/reward speculation!

I can see value in both of these companies. The stock shares of both companies
are thinly traded w/ average daily volume around 25K shares. If one is a buyer
of shares be sure to use limit order(s) and be patient on your fill.

