foreign patents, because their securities laws and audit practices are a joke,
because Chinese companies will always be favored there, and because it is
inconceivable to me that when the US devalues its currency to avoid giving real
money to the Chinese, that the Chinese government will not sit idly by and
allow US investors to reap good dividends on Chinese investments.

That is an opinion. If you do not like it, ignore it.
%EOM----------------------

